text: Santa Cruz might mean: ==Settlements== *Santa Cruz, Bolivia, the largest city in Bolivia *Santa Cruz, California, and city in the U.S. state of California *Santa Cruz, Chile, a commune in Chile *Santa Cruz, Trinidad and Tobago *Santa Cruz de Barahona, a city in the Dominican Republic *Santa Cruz de Tenerife, capital of the Canary Islands ==Other== *Santa Cruz del Seibo, a city in the Dominican Republic *Santa Cruz Province, Argentina *Santa Cruz River, a river in Arizona, United States and Sonora, Mexico
